        <abstract>
            <para>
                This book contains the course notes for Developing 
                the Service Tier with JavaEE/EJB and JBoss/Wildfly.
                This course provides background for service tier requirements
                and how they can be met with JavaEE/EJB technologies.
                This course covers development environment topics such as
                module layout, Maven and useful Maven plugins, IDE-integration, 
                and application-server management. 
            </para>
            <para>
                The material currently covers standards adopted as of 
                JavaEE 6 and is being actively updated with information
                from JavaEE 7.
            </para>
        </abstract>
    </bookinfo>
